PrometheusPraxisCodingTask2026v1
  taskid   PPX-TASK-0006
  title    Enforce non-actuation via CI and static checks
  priority P0
  status   PLANNED
  ownerteam Prometheus-Safety
  dependson [PPX-TASK-0001]
